<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 06:21:00 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>阿斯顿·马丁警告供应链利润下降和中国问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/aston-martin-warns-lower-profit-supply-chain-china-woes-2024-09-30/</link><description>英国豪华汽车制造商阿斯顿·马丁周一警告年度核心利润下降，并表示不再预计上半年实现正自由现金流，理由是供应链中断和中国市场疲软。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 06:10:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/aston-martin-warns-lower-profit-supply-chain-china-woes-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>Stellantis 发布盈利预警，援引全球市场和中国竞争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/stellantis-revises-guidance-downward-citing-performance-issues-industry-dynamics-2024-09-30/</link><description>Stellantis NV 周一下调了其指引，理由是全球行业动态恶化以及中国电动汽车竞争等因素。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 05:41:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/stellantis-revises-guidance-downward-citing-performance-issues-industry-dynamics-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，字节跳动计划使用华为芯片训练新的人工智能模型</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/bytedance-plans-new-ai-model-trained-with-huawei-chips-sources-say-2024-09-30/</link><description>三名知情人士表示，随着美国的限制措施迫使这家社交媒体巨头回国寻找芯片，TikTok 的中国母公司字节跳动计划开发一种主要使用同胞华为技术公司 (HWT.UL) 芯片训练的人工智能模型。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 05:33:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/bytedance-plans-new-ai-model-trained-with-huawei-chips-sources-say-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：日经指数回落，中国股市上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-09-30/</link><description>韦恩·科尔 (Wayne Cole) 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 04:33:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>白宫表示，拜登批准向台湾提供 5.67 亿美元的国防支持</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/biden-approves-567-mln-defense-support-taiwan-white-house-says-2024-09-30/</link><description>白宫称，美国总统乔·拜登周日批准向台湾提供 5.67 亿美元的防务支持，这是美国在与中国关系日益紧张的情况下加强台湾军事力量的最新举措。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 03:45:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/biden-approves-567-mln-defense-support-taiwan-white-house-says-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>波波维奇任命值得信赖的福克斯中尉为澳大利亚工作人员</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/popovic-appoints-trusted-lieutenant-foxe-australia-staff-2024-09-30/</link><description>格雷厄姆·阿诺德离开后，澳大利亚新任主帅托尼·波波维奇立即对澳大利亚队的教练队伍进行了彻底改革，任命长期担任副手的海登·福克斯和前队友保罗·奥肯担任助理教练。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 03:15:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/popovic-appoints-trusted-lieutenant-foxe-australia-staff-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>注重成本的中国游客寻求经济实惠的黄金周假期选择</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/cost-conscious-chinese-tourists-look-affordable-options-golden-week-holiday-2024-09-30/</link><description>旅游业专家表示，预计周二开始的黄金周假期期间，中国游客的旅行时间将比去年更长，但这并不一定会导致支出增加。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 03:04:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/cost-conscious-chinese-tourists-look-affordable-options-golden-week-holiday-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>越南特赦20名外国囚犯，其中包括中国和美国公民</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-offers-amnesty-20-foreign-prisoners-including-chinese-us-citizens-2024-09-30/</link><description>越南外交部副部长杜兴越周一表示，越南已赦免 20 名被监禁的外国人，其中包括 9 名中国公民和 2 名美国公民。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 02:41:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-offers-amnesty-20-foreign-prisoners-including-chinese-us-citizens-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>中国工厂、服务业活动下滑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-factory-service-sectors-skid-stimulus-calls-grow-2024-09-30/</link><description>中国的工厂活动连续第五个月萎缩，服务业在 9 月份大幅放缓，这表明北京将需要更多的刺激措施来实现 2024 年的增长目标，而今年只剩下三个月了。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 02:33:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-factory-service-sectors-skid-stimulus-calls-grow-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>财新PMI显示中国服务业活动放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-services-activity-slows-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-09-30/</link><description>周一的一项私营部门调查显示，尽管出口加速，但由于新业务增长触及近一年来的最低水平，中国服务业活动扩张在 9 月份放缓。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 01:57:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-services-activity-slows-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>中国房地产股因购房规则宽松和市场情绪改善而飙升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-property-shares-jump-easier-buying-restrictions-2024-09-30/</link><description>周一，中国房地产开发商的股价大幅上涨，涨幅达两位数，投资者对主要城市放宽的购房规定以及北京最新推出的刺激措施提振了低迷行业和经济的信心感到高兴。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 01:53:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-property-shares-jump-easier-buying-restrictions-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>财新PMI显示中国9月工厂活动显着降温</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-september-factory-activity-cools-notably-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-09-30/</link><description>周一的一项私营部门调查显示，由于国内外新订单降温，中国9月份制造业活动大幅萎缩，工厂主信心降至接近历史低点。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 01:50:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-september-factory-activity-cools-notably-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>中国9月份制造业活动连续第五个月下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-manufacturing-activity-declines-fifth-month-sept-2024-09-30/</link><description>周一官方工厂调查显示，中国 9 月份制造业活动连续第五个月萎缩，尽管增速低于 8 月份。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 01:39:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-manufacturing-activity-declines-fifth-month-sept-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>中国推出刺激措施，美元下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-steadies-dollar-slips-china-reaches-stimulus-2024-09-30/</link><description>由于日本即将上任的首相暗示货币政策应保持宽松，日元飙升周一企稳，而投资者对中国经济好转的希望推动商品货币升至年内高点。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 01:23:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-steadies-dollar-slips-china-reaches-stimulus-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>日经指数下跌，中国股市飙升，股价犹豫不决</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-30/</link><description>周一亚洲股市变得犹豫不决，因为中东的冲突抵消了中国更多政策措施的影响，而日经指数则因担心日本新首相支持利率正常化而下跌。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 00:28:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-30/</guid></item></channel></rss>